This release updates the SSH field to support the use of parameters and environment variables in configuration. For more details see the [documentation](https://docs.dagu.cloud/features/executors/ssh#dag-level-configuration).

## Changelog
* be57f3d9a18ea8e062b0435ed3b797addf89ca99 test(integration): verify containerName-only executor config works (#1248)

## What's Changed
* feat: Allow params & environment variables in SSH field by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1247
* test(integration): verify containerName-only executor config works by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1248


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/compare/v1.22.3...v1.22.4
